{"tid":683601,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"白宮重提500億美元關稅 中國：懇美方按聯合聲明精神而行","createTime":"2018-05-29T23:56:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-30T02:06:48.000Z","uid":53524,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"f0ce924dac46d99c65f8dbdce4a619a31b8b7ada","tid":683601,"uid":53524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T23:56:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2018/05/30/realtime/4807426.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2018%2F05%2F30%2Frealtime%2F4807426.jpg&h=115dd935&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國商務部對美國白宮發布的策略性聲明，既感到出乎意料，但亦在意料之中。<br />\n<br />\n商務部回應白宮重提向中國500億美元商品加徵25%關稅，計劃6月15日公布詳情。<br />\n<br />\n中國商務部認為，顯然有悖於不久前中美雙方在華盛頓達成的共識，無論美方出台甚麼舉措，中國都有信心、有能力、有經驗捍衛中國人民利益同國家核心利益。<br />\n<br />\n中國又敦促美國按照聯合聲明精神相向而行。"},{"pid":"160d3e03d1301a7d9f90735ed10f94edfa02477e","tid":683601,"uid":93986,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T23:58:29.000Z","msg":"口講<br />\n無論美方出台甚麼舉措，中國都有信心、有能力、有經驗捍衛中國人民利益同國家核心利益。<br />\n實際行動<br />\n無論美方出台甚麼舉措，中國都有信心、有能力、有經驗<span style=\"color: red;\">出賣</span>中國人民利益同國家核心利益。"},{"pid":"69d3fe3b557b0995dbf6b77b1ec9946e8560ac49","tid":683601,"uid":102096,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T23:58:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cec39c51694ad885a3f2384676d3757b813dfdf7","tid":683601,"uid":157138,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T23:59:57.000Z","msg":"美國：聯合聲明只係歷史文件 不再具有任何現實意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"437c2aa1f7f5a60866e2405d5bc90e106b9dd0d0","tid":683601,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cec39c51694ad885a3f2384676d3757b813dfdf7","tid":683601,"uid":157138,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T23:59:57.000Z","msg":"美國：聯合聲明只係歷史文件 不再具有任何現實意義<img src=\"/assets/f